OL,3,CLyra McKee trial shown shown footage
OL,4,Cof shot being fired
OL,6,FFootage from the final moments of Lyra
OL,7,FMcKee's life has been shown at the
OL,8,Ftrial of three men accused of
OL,9,Fmurdering the journalist.
OL,11,FVideo footage of shots being fired,
OL,12,Fincluding the shot which killed Ms
OL,13,FMcKee, were played during the trial at
OL,14,FBelfast Crown Court on Friday.
OL,16,FMs McKee, 29, died after being struck
OL,17,Fin the head by a bullet as she stood
OL,18,Fclose to police vehicles while
OL,19,Fobserving rioting in the Creggan area
OL,20,Fof Londonderry on the night of April
OL,21,F18 2019.
