OL,6,FThe three also face a number of other
OL,7,Fcharges, including riotous assembly,
OL,8,Fpossession of a firearm and ammunition
OL,9,Fwith intent, as well as possession of,
OL,10,Fand throwing of, petrol bombs.McIntyre
OL,11,Fis additionally charged with
OL,12,Fmembership of a proscribed
OL,13,Forganisation.
OL,15,FViolence had flared in Derry on the
OL,16,Fevening Ms McKee was killed after
OL,17,Fpolice entered the Creggan area to
OL,18,Fconduct searches.
