OL,6,FThe no-jury trial was shown video
OL,7,Ffootage from a PSNI evidence-gathering
OL,8,Fvehicle in Fanad Drive on the night Ms
OL,9,FMcKee after police had been attacked
OL,10,Fwith petrol bombs.
OL,12,FProsecuting barrister David McDowell
OL,13,Ftold the court that Ms McKee can be
OL,14,Fseen watching the disorder in the
OL,15,Ffootage.
OL,17,FHe said: "Just before 2303 hours,
OL,18,Fcheering can be heard which causes the
OL,19,Fcamera to pan back to the corner of
OL,20,Fthe crossroads."The first shot is
OL,21,Ffired five seconds later."
