OL,6,FHe added: "That first shot prompts the
OL,7,Fpolice evidence gathering camera to
OL,8,Fpan in on a gunman on the corner from
OL,9,Fwhere the attack on police had been
OL,10,Fcarried out.
OL,12,F"He can then be seen firing a second
OL,13,Fshot from a handgun."
OL,15,FMr McDowell said there then appeared
OL,16,Fto be three misfires.
OL,18,FHe added: "He then succeeds in firing
OL,19,Ftwo further shots.
