OL,6,F"It is only after the fourth shot,
OL,7,Fsome 20 seconds after the first, that
OL,8,Fscreaming can be heard indicating that
OL,9,FMs McKee has been struck by a bullet.
OL,11,F"This tends to indicate she was struck
OL,12,Fby one of the last two rounds, most
OL,13,Flikely the final shot."
OL,15,FMr McDowell added: "The driver of the
OL,16,Fevidence gathering vehicle reports
OL,17,Fthat at around 2300 hours he saw the
OL,18,Fcrowd turn their attention in the
OL,19,Fdirection of the shots.
