OL,6,F"He then saw a gunman appear at the
OL,7,Fjunction and fire at least four shots
OL,8,Ftowards the police vehicles.
OL,10,F"He saw that a woman who had been
OL,11,Fstanding to the side of one of the
OL,12,Fpolice Land Rovers had fallen to the
OL,13,Fground and he heard another woman
OL,14,Fscreaming for help.
OL,16,F"Assistance came from police and
OL,17,Fmembers of the public."
OL,19,FThe barrister told the court that
OL,20,Fofficers in Land Rovers had reported
OL,21,Fhearing bullets strike their vehicles.
