OL,6,FThe court was then played footage from
OL,7,Fa mobile phone which had been seized
OL,8,Fby police.
OL,10,FMr McDowell said this showed, in the
OL,11,Fmoments before the shooting, four
OL,12,Fmasked men walk to the scene, one
OL,13,Fcarrying a handgun.
OL,15,FHe said: "A few seconds later police
OL,16,Fsend up a flare when it is realised
OL,17,Fthat Ms McKee has been injured.
OL,19,F"She was taken to hospital in one of
OL,20,Fthe police Land Rovers but death was
OL,21,Fconfirmed just after her arrival."
